## ⚙️ Konfiguracija

**Docker Compose environment varijable:**
```yaml
environment:
  DB_HOST: mysql-follow
  DB_USER: root
  DB_PASSWORD: root
  DB_NAME: follow_service
  PORT: 3004
  USER_INFO_SERVICE_URL: http://user-info:3013
```

